# Request for Proposal (RFP) to Install Basement UPS System at AAFC-Guelph Research and Development Centre
## Solicitation Number: 01B46-23-154

The Agriculture and Agri-Food Canada (AAFC) department is seeking contractors to provide construction services for installing a UPS (Uninterruptible Power Supply) system and allied equipment at the Guelph Research and Development Centre (GRDC) in Guelph, Ontario.

## Project Details

* **Reference Number:** cb-138-13958617
* **Amendment Number:** 9
* **Solicitation Number:** 01B46-23-154
* **Publication Date:** October 13, 2023
* **Tender Closing Date:** November 6, 2023, 2:00 PM (Eastern Standard Time)
* **Expected Contract Start Date:** November 10, 2023
* **Expected Contract End Date:** March 31, 2024

## Scope of Work

The successful contractor shall provide and install a UPS system and associated equipment at the GRDC. The work must be completed by March 31, 2024. It is essential that the contractor considers the construction methods necessary to complete the project during the winter months.

## Optional Site Visit

An optional site visit is scheduled for October 19th at 10:30 AM at the GRDC. This visit is an opportunity for contractors to inspect the site and ask questions.

## Information Requests

All information requests and inquiries related to this RFP must be directed to the Contract Officer, Jacques Toussaint, in writing via email at [jacques.toussaint@agr.gc.ca](mailto:jacques.toussaint@agr.gc.ca). Suppliers are advised that contacting any other person may lead to disqualification.

## Proposal Evaluation

AAFC reserves the right to accept any proposal in whole or in part, without prior negotiation, and to reject any or all proposals received.

## Contact Information

Jacques Toussaint  
Agent de Contrats  
Agriculture and Agri-Food Canada - Eastern Service Center  
2001 Robert-Bourassa, Pièce 671-TEN  
Montréal, QC H3A 3N2  
Tel.: (438) 455 8237  
Email: [jacques.toussaint@agr.gc.ca](mailto:jacques.toussaint@agr.gc.ca)  

## Tenders and Attachments

Tenders must be submitted
